Pizza Bianca

For the pizza dough:

500 grams all-purpose flour
8 grams instant or active dry yeast
7 grams sea salt
338 grams warm water
13 grams olive oil
Semolina flour or cornmeal

For the sauce and topping:

100 gr whole milk ricotta cheese
sea salt, to taste
Fresh ground black pepper
1/2 small garlic clove
50 gr shredded mozzarella cheese
50 gr shredded Parmesan cheese
Dried or fresh oregano, and red pepper flakes
